title: MAR 02 2022 - RUSSIA ADVANCES AS BIDEN STUMBLES
description:
Ukraine is a warzone! Russia takes over Kherson, Ukraine, street fighting erupts in multiple Ukrainian cities, and Kharkiv has turned into a bombed wasteland. Jack Posobiec reacts to Biden’s State of the Union address, meanwhile the House Committee is investigating January 6 and has subpoenaed a lawyer who has been in contact with Donald Trump. Lastly, it has been revealed that President Biden’s Supreme Court nominee, Judge Jackson, once argued that the judicial system is ‘unfair’ towards sexual predators.
Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
